<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H2><CENTER>Report of the <BR>
Fifth International Expert Seminar on <BR>
Building Non-Handicapping Environments: <BR>
Access Legislation and Design Solutions <BR>
<IMG SRC="../AfricanHut.gif" BORDER="0" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" HEIGHT="293"
WIDTH="252" ALIGN="BOTTOM"> <BR>
Harare, Zimbabwe, January 16-18, 1992 <A NAME="anchor52685"></A><BR>
