NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> Legal instruments should be developed to ensure accessibility both
in new construction and in renovating, upgrading and expanding existing
urban environments. <BR>
<BR>
3.<IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> <IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> <IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> <IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> <IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> In recognition of their experience, disabled people and their 
organizations
should be actively involved at all levels in drafting, monitoring and 
enforcing
legal instruments for the planning and building process. <BR>
<BR>
4.<IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> <IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
