NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> Governments should provide funding for consumer organizations to 
allow
them to build up their expertise in this area and to participate in the
decision making and implementation of these instruments. <BR>
<BR>
6.<IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> <IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> <IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
