Bilaga 1 
<H2><CENTER>Reflection Group's Report<BR>
<BR>
Messina 2nd June 1995</CENTER>
</H2>
<P><CENTER><HR></CENTER>
<P>Part One: A Strategy for Europe<BR>
<BR>
The Challenge<BR>
The Response<BR>
The 1996 Conference<BR>
