<BR>
<H2><CENTER>Minutes of ENIL&#180;s Board Meeting on June 11, 
1996</CENTER>
</H2>
<BR>
<BR>
Board members present:<BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>Manfred Srb, Austria; <BR>
Regina Reichert, Germany; <BR>
Bente Skansg&aring;rd, Norway; <BR>
Adolf Ratzka, Sweden; <BR>
John Evans, UK.</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<BR>
1. Election of officers for the meeting<BR>
The following officers for the meeting were elected by the Board<BR>
John Evans, chair; Adolf Ratzka, minute taker.<BR>
<BR>
2. Right to sign on behalf of ENIL<BR>
The Board delegated the responsibility to sign on behalf of ENIL to John
Evans and Adolf Ratzka, individually, where the right to sign on 
financial
matters can be delegated to a third person, if needed.<BR>
<BR>
3. Election of ENIL&#180;s chairperson and secretary<BR>
The Board elected among themselves John Evans as chairperson. Adolf 
Ratzka
was elected secretary under the condition that STIL supplies the 
necessary
secretarial support.<BR>
<BR>
4. Immediate adoption of the minutes<BR>
The Board decided to immediately adopt the minutes of the present Board
meeting.<BR>
<BR>
