<H3><CENTER><BR>
ENIL meeting in Stockholm, June 9-11, 1996</CENTER>
</H3>
<H4><CENTER>Venue Servicehus M&auml;lteriet on Island Reimersholmen, 
Stockholm<BR>
Program</CENTER>
</H4>
Sunday, June 9<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
10:00<IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"><IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"><IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"><IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"><IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"><IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"><IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3">Opening<BR>
10:15<IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"><IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"><IMG SRC="../Pixel1x1.gif" WIDTH="1" HEIGHT="1" ALIGN="BOTTOM" 
