Ashanti,
unpublished Post-graduate Diploma Design Thesis, Department of 
Architecture,
University of Science and Technology, Kumasi, Ghana.<BR>
<BR>
Ministry of Works and Housing (1988) Ghana Building Regulations.<BR>
