<TITLE>Taylor &amp  Francis Tables of Contents Listservers</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" TEXT="000000">
<BR>
<CENTER><H3>Tables of Contents Listservers</H3>
<H4>Taylor &amp  Francis and Psychology Press journals</H4></CENTER>
<BR>
<BR>
<HR>
<H4>A Free Service</H4>
<H4>Details of forthcoming papers e-mailed to you direct on your 
chosen journal or subject area!</H4>
<BR>
<HR>
These Taylor &amp  Francis listservers will enable you to automatically receive Tables of Contents of 
journals at regular intervals - before they appear in print.<BR>
<BR>
The layout of each Table of Contents is simple to follow -  and access couldn't be easier.  Instructions on 
joining the Table of Contents listservers,  using this service,  and  a list of available listservers  can be 
obtained by simply  sending  the following e-mail message.  Send the message to the following 
address:<BR>
<BR>
<H4>MAILSERV@TANDF.CO.UK</H4>
with the subject heading left blank, and type in the body of the message:<BR>
<H4>HELP</H4>
<BR>
<BR>
<B>N.B. Make sure you are NOT using an e-mail signature when sending messages to the 
listserv.</B><BR><B>
</B><BR>
<UL>
<LI>For regular updates on continuing developments, keep visiting our Home Page!
</UL>
<BR>
<HR>
Return to the <A HREF = "../default.htm">Home Page</A> <BR>
To send any enquiries via email   <A HREF = "mailto:mmorrow@tandf.co.uk">click here</A>   <BR>
