<HTML>
<TITLE>TOXICOLOGY METHODS</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" TEXT="000000">
<BR>
<CENTER><H1>Toxicology Methods</H1>
<IMG BORDER = 1 SRC = "../txm.gif" ></CENTER><BR>
<H3>EDITOR</H3>
<B>Shayne C Gold PhD</B><BR><B>
</B>Consulting Toxicologist,<BR>
1818 White Oak Road, Raleigh,<BR>
NC 27608, USA<BR>
<BR>
<H3>SCOPE</H3>
While toxicology progresses in its understanding of the mechanisms underlying the toxicities of the 
modern environment, most literature in the field remains focused on communicating current knowledge of 
these mechanisms rather than assessing new ways of studying them.<BR>
<I>Toxicology Methods</I> provides a peer reviewed forum for both sharing and critically evaluating 
new methods, techniques, equipment, and experimental design, as well as for documenting the emergence 
of innovative applications of existing methods and techniques. These can include new computer programs, 
mathematical models, approaches to refining and validating pharmacodynamic models, and approaches to 
the analysis of data.  Of equal interest are in vivo models with alternative species, in vitro models at the 
chemical, biochemical, molecular. cellular, and organ level, new applications of existing instruments (such 
as NMR or MRI as nondestructive/non-invasive means of assessing activity or effects in intact, functioning 
organisms), and novel approaches to risk evaluation.<BR>
Published papers, which range from short letters and technical notes to long technology reviews solicited to 
appear twice a year are judged on their value regarding how they can or might be used as new tools for 
toxicologists.<BR>
<BR>
<H3>SUBSCRIPTION INFORMATION</H3>
Vol 6 (1996) Quarterly<BR>
ISSN 1051-7235<BR>
Institutional: US$298  /  £180<BR>
Personal: US$94  /  £57<BR>
<BR>
<H3>JOURNALS OF RELATED INTEREST</H3>
<A HREF = "bmk.htm">Biomarkers</A> , <A HREF = "txs.htm">Toxic Substance Mechanisms</A> , 
<A HREF = "teh.htm">Toxicology &amp  Environmental Health</A> , <A HREF = 
"ten.htm">Toxicology &amp  Ecotoxicology News</A>  <BR>
<BR>
<H3>SAMPLE COPY REQUEST</H3>
To request a sample copy of this journal please <A HREF = "mailto:adaly@tandf.co.uk">click here</A>  <BR>
<BR>
